{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "You are a Go engineer working on a Kubernetes operator.\nThe repository is located at /Users/kpais/kpais-workspace/a_b_evals/repos/cert-manager-operator-treatment.\nChange your working directory to that repository before beginning.\n\nTask:\nAdd a tlsMinVersion field to IstioCSRConfig in api/operator/v1alpha1/istiocsr_types.go.\nApply two CEL validation rules:\n1. Presence-immutability: once set, the field cannot be removed; once unset, it cannot be added\n2. Value-immutability: self == oldSelf when the field is set\n\nAdd an enum constraint restricting valid values to VersionTLS12 and VersionTLS13.\n\nUpdate the mutation pipeline in pkg/controller/istiocsr/deployments.go to pass the\nvalue as a --tls-min-version flag to the IstioCSR container.\n\n\nProduce a complete implementation. Include:\n- All files that must be modified with the exact changes\n- Any make targets or commands to run and in what order\n- The complete code for any new files or functions"}, "timestamp": "2026-07-20T18:02:27.333Z"}
